OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome heavy
OL,6,Fand perhaps thundery showers this
OL,7,Fevening in north, mainly Angus, these
OL,8,Fturning lighter and more scattered
OL,9,Ftonight with a few clear intervals
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA bright start with just
OL,13,Fthe odd shower. Turning cloudier in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon with some outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FChangeable through this period with a
OL,19,Fmix of bright spells and showers,
OL,20,Fthese heavy and thundery over Tayside
OL,21,Fon Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
